video.title: Forensic Files
video.synopsis: Detectives and crime lab technicians use the latest and most fascinating procedures to solve crimes in this documentary-style show.

episodes.synopsis: After a woman dies in a car fire, police suspect she was murdered. But two different fire investigators come to two very different conclusions.
episodes.title: Plastic Fire

episodes.synopsis: A woman writes her last will and testament immediately before being killed. A clue in the document helps police identify and convict the culprit.
episodes.title: Last Will

episodes.synopsis: After a man dies of an apparent heart attack, police suspect his girlfriend may have had a role. But some toxicology experts see another possibility.
episodes.title: Dessert Served Cold

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is murdered, police discover an unusual bite pattern that leads them to a suspect, who is convicted but maintains his innocence.
episodes.title: Once Bitten

episodes.synopsis: A pregnant woman is found murdered in her home. Police notice an odd similarity between the circumstances of her death and the plot of a movie.
episodes.title: Dinner and a Movie

episodes.synopsis: A man claims a stalker killed his wife and is dubbed a hero for trying to protect her. But years later, new evidence paints a very different picture.
episodes.title: A Welcome Intrusion

episodes.synopsis: A police officer and his wife have an argument and a shotgun goes off, killing her. A jury must determine if this was murder or suicide.
episodes.title: Within Arm's Reach

episodes.synopsis: After a 10-year-old girl is found murdered near her small Alaska town, police discover that one man's alibi isn't as solid as it first appears.
episodes.title: Sphere of Influence

episodes.synopsis: A serial killer stalks New York and sends cryptic clues to the newspaper. Astronomers and handwriting experts work together to catch the murderer.
episodes.title: Sign of the Zodiac

episodes.synopsis: The owner of a junkyard is shot to death in his office, and police find the crime scene oddly clean. The wife's computer is a very different story.
episodes.title: Web of Seduction

episodes.synopsis: After traces of arsenic are found in a woman's bone marrow, investigators must determine what or who is responsible for the poisoning.
episodes.title: Bad Medicine

episodes.synopsis: A retired couple's murder goes unsolved for years before a forensic scientist takes it upon himself to uncover long overlooked evidence.
episodes.title: Over a Barrel

episodes.synopsis: After the wife of an Air Force serviceman is killed, investigators attempt to reassemble a shredded computer disk in hopes of finding the killer.
episodes.title: Shear Luck

episodes.synopsis: A highway patrolman has a hunch that the deadly traffic accident he discovered masks a much darker story, but the coroner sees it differently.
episodes.title: Crash Course

episodes.synopsis: A murderer leaves DNA at the scene but the profile doesn't match anyone on record. Forensic scientists use the DNA to paint a picture of the suspect.
episodes.title: Tight-Fitting Genes

episodes.synopsis: An architect dies shortly before she's scheduled to testify in a criminal trial. After an autopsy shows arsenic poisoning, police search for a killer.
episodes.title: Writer's Block

episodes.synopsis: A man is killed in his garage and his wife is injured in the attack. Forensic evidence points investigators toward a twisted plot of lust and greed.
episodes.title: Sunday School Ambush

episodes.synopsis: To catch a serial killer, investigators must rely on a new forensic technique that tests cremated remains for signs of foul play.
episodes.title: Penchant for Poison

episodes.synopsis: After a woman dies in a car crash, the scene looks like a tragic accident. But when footprints are discovered, the investigation takes a darker turn.
episodes.title: Naughty or Nyce

episodes.synopsis: When a young girl falls ill and dies, authorities travel halfway around the world to search for evidence that will shed light on the tragic death.
episodes.title: Sunday's Wake

episodes.synopsis: A young woman is murdered and police find little evidence. Forensic investigators must use a breakthrough technique to catch the killer.
episodes.title: Nice Threads

episodes.synopsis: Police investigate a woman's disappearance and discover clues in the family computer that point directly toward her killer.
episodes.title: Internal Affair

episodes.synopsis: After a 12-year-old girl claims to have been abducted and assaulted, police find her account hard to believe. Forensic evidence backs up her story.
episodes.title: Van-ished

episodes.synopsis: Investigators discover that an envelope's manufacturing flaw may lead them to a murderer willing to kill strangers to get at his intended target.
episodes.title: Water Hazard

episodes.synopsis: A man claims that a robber shot and killed his wife while on the beach. Investigators grow suspicious after learning about a song he'd downloaded.
episodes.title: As the Tide Turns

episodes.synopsis: A murder in Australia baffles police until they discover a device that serves as a unique witness in this landmark forensic case.
episodes.title: Ticker Tape

episodes.synopsis: The deaths of a firefighter and police officer occurred years apart and in different towns. The connection: Both men were married to the same woman.
episodes.title: Cold Hearted

episodes.synopsis: A woman is attacked and dials 911, but dies before police arrive. Investigators call on a forensic optometrist to help them identify the killer.
episodes.title: Quite a Spectacle

episodes.synopsis: After a dedicated teacher stops showing up to school, police must determine if she's simply gone on vacation or fallen victim to foul play.
episodes.title: Transaction Failed

episodes.synopsis: Experts question whether a woman really committed suicide after a forensic pathologist and investigators make several startling discoveries.
episodes.title: Insignificant Others

episodes.synopsis: Two years after a 13-year-old girl goes missing from her Colorado home, a latent print examiner takes on the case and makes a crucial discovery.
episodes.title: Screen Pass

episodes.synopsis: A man is convicted of killing a social worker and setting her home ablaze. He maintains his innocence and attempts to solve the case from prison.
episodes.title: Freedom Fighter

episodes.synopsis: A man is convicted of killing a woman and attacking a 6-year-old, but his wife remains convinced of his innocence and sets out to prove it.
episodes.title: All Butt Certain

episodes.synopsis: A prominent Nevada politician's sudden death leaves authorities searching for the cause. Tiny puncture wounds found during the autopsy provide a clue.
episodes.title: Political Thriller

episodes.synopsis: A couple returns from dinner to find an intruder in their apartment. In the ensuing murder investigation, police discover a shocking recording.
episodes.title: Double Cross

episodes.synopsis: After a man is stabbed to death and his girlfriend assaulted, police discover odd impressions in the dirt outside the couple's bedroom window.
episodes.title: Window Watcher

episodes.synopsis: A young mother and her infant son disappear along with their vehicle in broad daylight. When a witness reports a carjacking, police race to help.
episodes.title: Kidnapping

episodes.synopsis: A young woman is strangled to death. Seeking a suspect, police focus on a connection between this murder and another from years earlier.
episodes.title: Calculated Coincidence

episodes.synopsis: A serial rapist's sexual assaults grow more and more brutal, pushing police to do all they can to find the perpetrator before he strikes again.
episodes.title: Unmasked

episodes.synopsis: A woman is stabbed, raped and left for dead, but survives. She gives a vivid description, but things take a surprising turn when a suspect confesses.
episodes.title: Smiley Face

episodes.synopsis: A successful businessman is murdered in his home. Initially, police suspect an intruder, but racy evidence points to another possibility.
episodes.title: Dirty Laundry

episodes.synopsis: A family vacation turns deadly when the wife falls to her death. Investigators must determine if this was a suicide, an accident or something else.
episodes.title: Drowning Sorrows

episodes.synopsis: When a scientist mysteriously dies, investigators analyze his hair in the hopes of nailing down a timeline and discovering if he was poisoned.
episodes.title: Hair Line

episodes.synopsis: A Florida waitress vanishes and is then found murdered. Suspicions turn to a neighbor who exhibits odd behavior toward reporters covering the crime.
episodes.title: Pet Rock

episodes.synopsis: After an exotic dancer goes missing, police focus their investigation on a local businessman, who tries to throw cadaver dogs off the scent.
episodes.title: Best Foot Forward

episodes.synopsis: A teacher fails to show up to class and her husband finds her dead at their home. What first looks like an accident quickly turns sinister.
episodes.title: Hell's Kitchen

episodes.synopsis: After a man is found dead in his bedroom, his wife insists he committed suicide. But when police investigate, they make a shocking discovery.
episodes.title: Freeze Framed

episodes.synopsis: When a series of bodies are found dismembered in different locations, police rely on a new technology to help solve a case that's gone cold.
episodes.title: Touch of Evil

episodes.synopsis: The first instance of DNA profiling sets one man free from prison and helps identify the real culprit, who killed five women in Virginia.
episodes.title: Southside Strangler

episodes.synopsis: After 180 people contract pneumonia-like symptoms in Philadelphia, one scientist helps launch an extensive medical investigation to discover why.
episodes.title: Legionnaires' Disease

episodes.synopsis: After an exotic dancer is murdered in Florida, investigators use a small piece of thread to connect the killer to that crime and many more.
episodes.title: The Common Thread

episodes.synopsis: When a woman exhibits strange flu-like symptoms, doctors are flummoxed. After investigators notice an unusual clue, the case takes a sinister turn.
episodes.title: Bitter Potion

episodes.synopsis: When dozens of infants develop serious breathing problems in the Cleveland area, doctors and investigators search high and low for the cause.
episodes.title: Fatal Fungus

episodes.synopsis: A well-liked bank vice president collapses and dies after taking pain pills laced with cyanide. The search for a motive reveals a callous suspect.
episodes.title: Something's Fishy

episodes.synopsis: After an 11-month-old boy suddenly dies, investigators find suspicious clues in his liver that send them on a frantic search for the cause of death.
episodes.title: Without a Trace

episodes.synopsis: Several murders are clearly committed by the same man. When one potential victim escapes, the authorities are finally able to track the killer.
episodes.title: Knot for Everyone

episodes.synopsis: Was it a tragic shooting accident or something far worse? It takes investigators 20 years to answer what happened one fateful day in 1976.
episodes.title: Grave Evidence

episodes.synopsis: After a 4-month-old child mysteriously dies, his mother is convicted. Investigators must re-evaluate their case when new evidence comes to light.
episodes.title: Deadly Formula

episodes.synopsis: Brain seizures and breathing problems put a 2-year-old in the hospital. Doctors are baffled until they learn of a rare syndrome in the family.
episodes.title: Broken Bond

episodes.synopsis: After a deadly and mysterious house fire kills two family members, investigators discover evidence that points to a cold-blooded plot.
episodes.title: Ultimate Betrayal

episodes.synopsis: After a 5-year-old girl disappears from a neighborhood Christmas party, forensic investigators close in on a suspect thanks to fiber analysis.
episodes.title: Innocence Lost

episodes.synopsis: A man in intense pain checks into the hospital, but he deteriorates. Something he's being given in the hospital isn't curing him, it's poisoning him.
episodes.title: Till Death Do Us Part

episodes.synopsis: Police track the killer of two adolescent boys by using profiling, hypnosis and a scientific analysis of the rope used during the crimes.
episodes.title: Ties That Bind

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is found dead in her basement, police question if it was an accident or murder. Only when the scene is re-created does it become clear.
episodes.title: Accident or Murder?

episodes.synopsis: When more than a dozen children contract a mysterious and deadly illness in Seattle, medical investigators frantically search for a cause and cure.
episodes.title: Core Evidence

episodes.synopsis: After the baffling deaths of more than 20 people on an Indian reservation, Navajo medicine men provide a clue that leads to a most unlikely killer.
episodes.title: With Every Breath

episodes.synopsis: Baffled as to how to identify and stop a serial rapist, police turn to geographical profiling in hopes of narrowing in on a suspect.
episodes.title: Badge of Deceit

episodes.synopsis: When a woman and her infant son are found dead, the evidence points toward the victim's husband. However, strands of hair reveal another possibility.
episodes.title: A Woman Scorned

episodes.synopsis: After a decomposed body is discovered in a steel drum, investigators find a badly damaged address book that may reveal the victim and her killer.
episodes.title: A Voice from Beyond

episodes.synopsis: After a young child dies, police investigate a local hospital where the pediatric mortality rate is far higher than anywhere else in the country.
episodes.title: Nursery Crimes

episodes.synopsis: After a young girl is found dead in her backyard, her parents insist that a pack of dogs was responsible. However, detectives have their doubts.
episodes.title: Man's Best Friend?

episodes.synopsis: A young woman is brutally murdered in her apartment. Investigators have little to go on except for a small smear of blood that may hide a fingerprint.
episodes.title: Soft Touch

episodes.synopsis: An investigation into a model's death points toward a photographer, who claims the woman died during a consensual sexual encounter gone wrong.
episodes.title: Photo Finish

episodes.synopsis: Florida police finally catch a break when they discover that the serial killer they're searching for has an unusual dog with an unusual habit.
episodes.title: Treads and Threads

episodes.synopsis: A woman accuses her doctor of rape, but blood tests suggest otherwise. Investigators learn that in some cases, not even DNA is what it seems.
episodes.title: Bad Blood

episodes.synopsis: A woman is charged in her husband's death, which initially appeared to be a suicide. Later, the woman's son vows to discover the truth.
episodes.title: Where the Blood Drops

episodes.synopsis: NASA technology, a common housefly and the family cat collectively help to solve a woman's sudden disappearance in a most unusual way.
episodes.title: Cats, Flies & Snapshots

episodes.synopsis: When two men confess to the same horrific crime, investigators must use forensic evidence to determine who's lying and who's telling the truth.
episodes.title: Forever Hold Your Peace

episodes.synopsis: After two boys are brutally attacked and left for dead, investigators use water from a nearby pond to help identify and convict the criminals.
episodes.title: Reel Danger

episodes.synopsis: Tiny hairs discovered on a murdered woman's jacket point investigators to a suspect in this landmark case for forensic science.
episodes.title: Purr-fect Match

episodes.synopsis: Investigators offer a harrowing behind-the-scenes look at the nearly catastrophic 1984 Rajneeshee bioterror attack in rural Oregon.
episodes.title: Bio-Attack

episodes.synopsis: After a woman is killed by a single gunshot, two sets of scientists offer differing interpretations of the forensic evidence.
episodes.title: A Shot in the Dark

episodes.synopsis: When the founder of American Atheists vanishes, the investigation homes in on several suspects, including one of the organization's own employees.
episodes.title: Without a Prayer

episodes.synopsis: Forensics and quick thinking on the part of the victim help investigators identify the man responsible for her kidnapping and assault.
episodes.title: A Touching Recollection

episodes.synopsis: Three victims all identify the same man as their rapist, but the DNA disagrees. It would take years before authorities could right a horrible wrong.
episodes.title: Within a Hair

episodes.synopsis: When a couple is murdered, police initially suspect a drug deal gone bad. However, evidence found on the couple's dog tells a different story.
episodes.title: Chief Evidence

episodes.synopsis: A woman grows suspicious that her seemingly perfect mate is slowly poisoning her. Determined to prove his guilt, she sets a clever trap.
episodes.title: A Bitter Pill to Swallow

episodes.synopsis: Police use evidence found on a discarded coffee cup to help identify the man responsible for a string of unsolved murders in Wichita Falls, Texas.
episodes.title: Sip of Sins

episodes.synopsis: When a college student's car is found abandoned, bloody and still running, investigators must use DNA to connect the victim to her killer.
episodes.title: Telltale Tracks

episodes.synopsis: After a pastor's wife drowns in the bathtub, investigators find an unprescribed drug in her bloodstream along with a series of troubling web searches.
episodes.title: Ghost in the Machine

episodes.synopsis: Shortly after opening a car restoration business, the owner becomes seriously ill. Investigators suspect that a business partner may be responsible.
episodes.title: The Metal Business

episodes.synopsis: After an Alaska woman is found murdered, detectives use an unusual clue left at the scene of the crime to help bring a killer to justice.
episodes.title: Palm Print Conviction

episodes.synopsis: The murder of a 9-year-old girl goes unsolved until investigators use cutting-edge audio technology to connect a suspect to the crime.
episodes.title: A Bag of Evidence

episodes.synopsis: After a young woman is abducted, forensic investigators find charred remains that help them to identify both the victim and the murderer.
episodes.title: Tooth or Consequences

episodes.synopsis: The mystery behind a deadly string of Seattle-area arsons is finally solved thanks to forensic hypnosis, behavioral profiling and a piece of art.
episodes.title: Fire Proof

episodes.synopsis: When a young boy develops serious respiratory problems and his father shows signs of early Alzheimer's disease, investigators search for the cause.
episodes.title: Breaking the Mold

episodes.synopsis: When two gay rights activists are brutally murdered, investigators assume it was a hate crime. But the true motive proves much more complicated.
episodes.title: Printed Proof

episodes.synopsis: Forensics revealed the race and age of remains found in marshlands, but a special consultant was needed to digitally reconstruct the victim's face.
episodes.title: About Face

episodes.synopsis: A killer stuffs incriminating evidence into a plastic bag and throws it into the river, but his plan backfires when the bag gets caught in a tree.
episodes.title: In the Bag

episodes.synopsis: Days after a woman sells her home and moves into a small trailer, she dies in a fire that destroys her new home. But it may not have been an accident.
episodes.title: Yes, In Deed

episodes.synopsis: A cold case investigator finds a key clue, on the sole of the victim's boot, that will help solve the 14-year-old murder of a security guard.
episodes.title: Guarded Secrets

episodes.synopsis: After 25 years, investigators are able to use evidence from a cigarette to lead them to a man responsible for a series of rapes and murders.
episodes.title: Smoking Out a Killer

episodes.synopsis: Evidence found on top of a frozen river provides a big break in the investigation of the murder of a woman killed at the business she owned.
episodes.title: Frozen Assets

episodes.synopsis: Forensic hypnosis helps investigators create a composite sketch of a murder suspect using the subconscious memories of an unsure witness.
episodes.title: House Hunting

episodes.synopsis: When a teenager comes home to find his father dead in a pool of blood, footprints left in the snow outside might be the clue that leads to the killer.
episodes.title: Shoot to Thrill

episodes.synopsis: DNA evidence suggested that a man found dead in his Iowa home was murdered by a woman, and a strange story told in an unrelated arrest leads to her.
episodes.title: Dancing with the Devil

episodes.synopsis: Police suspect suicide when a young woman's body is found under a bridge, but evidence suggests she was actually thrown to her death.
episodes.title: Last Dance

episodes.synopsis: Finding a killer's DNA among a giant pool of blood left behind from 46 stab wounds in a construction manager's body proves difficult.
episodes.title: Constructive Criticism

episodes.synopsis: After he reports the shooting of his wife, a man becomes the prime suspect in the crime. But further analysis points investigators in a new direction.
episodes.title: Home Evasion

episodes.synopsis: Police doubt the story of a man who claims his mother was killed by a hitchhiker, and they turn to science to challenge his version of events.
episodes.title: Stranger in the Night

episodes.synopsis: A jacket found near a pool of blood is traced to a woman whose screams from a truck were misinterpreted as wild fun rather than cries for help.
episodes.title: As Fault

episodes.synopsis: An man with an axe butchers a court clerk and leaves his wife barely alive, and evidence collected hundreds of miles away may lead to the killer.
episodes.title: Family Ties

episodes.synopsis: Two men who live together are potentially linked to the same murder, and clues from beer bottles could help figure out which one of them is a killer.
episodes.title: Trouble Brewing

episodes.synopsis: In a race to stop a serial bomber who's attacked two churches before he strikes again, investigators pin their hopes on following a copper wire.
episodes.title: Holy Terror

episodes.synopsis: When a seemingly healthy college student turns up dead, investigators struggle to figure out why. But tiny clues start to shed some light.
episodes.title: Needle in a Haystack

episodes.synopsis: After discovering the body of a female college student who had been stabbed more than 100 times, investigators try to determine if it was a sex crime.
episodes.title: Room with a View

episodes.synopsis: Investigators create a composite sketch of a man whose body is burned beyond recognition, and decades-old building materials provide key clues.
episodes.title: Dollars and Sense

episodes.synopsis: When an abandoned car is found full of bullet holes, a microscopic clue provides the path to learning what happened to the missing driver.
episodes.title: All That Glitters Is Gold

episodes.synopsis: A teenage girl is found dead on the side of the road with her throat slit, and one hair left in a defensive wound could reveal her killer's identity.
episodes.title: Deadly Rebellion

episodes.synopsis: When two women who live in the same apartment complex are murdered, police believe they are looking for one killer with a deep hatred of women.
episodes.title: Sign of the Crime

episodes.synopsis: An officer believes the disappearance of a female college student is connected to a woman's body found hundreds of miles away in a barn fire.
episodes.title: Covet Thy Neighbor

episodes.synopsis: As she was dying, a woman wrote a name on a wall in her own blood. Though it's assumed it would be the name of her killer, the case isn't that simple.
episodes.title: Writing on the Wall

episodes.synopsis: A murderer took off with a load of cash after killing a manager at a steakhouse, but investigators believe the suspect knew his victim.
episodes.title: Hundreds of Reasons

episodes.synopsis: Nearly two decades after a young woman was raped and murdered, a cold case squad in Florida uses advancements in forensic science to nab the killer.
episodes.title: Cold Feet

episodes.synopsis: The search for a killer who left a man's burned body in a parking lot leads investigators to security camera footage that reveals his identity.
episodes.title: Separation Anxiety

episodes.synopsis: Investigators rely on DNA evidence found under a dead female college student's fingernails to find the man who strangled her to death.
episodes.title: Low Maintenance

episodes.synopsis: A woman and her soon-to-be ex-husband are murdered in their home, and the killer takes a computer that holds the key clues to solving the crime.
episodes.title: Fate Date

episodes.synopsis: Police hit a dead end when investigating the case of a woman who was murdered while jogging and talking to her husband on a cell phone.
episodes.title: Trail of a Killer

episodes.synopsis: After a man is found dead by his wife, police compile circumstantial evidence implicating her. But the key evidence is a bullet fired years ago.
episodes.title: Gone Ballistic

episodes.synopsis: When a body found stuffed in a suitcase resembles that of another victim, a suspect in both killings emerges alongside motives of power and control.
episodes.title: Seeing Red

episodes.synopsis: When a nursing student goes missing, investigators find her car, which contains the key to an unknown location that could provide important clues.
episodes.title: Skeleton Key

episodes.synopsis: When a funeral director is shot to death, investigators initially suspect his son. Instead, a mask found near the scene provides important clues.
episodes.title: Funeral Services

episodes.synopsis: A killer who carefully cleaned his crime scene strikes again three years later and leaves behind clues that can prove he committed both crimes.
episodes.title: Expert Witness

episodes.synopsis: Investigators differ on the cause of a crash near Yosemite National Park between a car of Secret Service agents and one driven by a local deputy.
episodes.title: Deadly Curve

episodes.synopsis: Investigators look for clues to determine what caused the worst train disaster in U.S. history, a 1993 Amtrak crash that killed 47 people.
episodes.title: Visibility Zero

episodes.synopsis: Arson investigators find the cause of a fire that killed 31 people in a subway station, but technology is needed to determine why it became so deadly.
episodes.title: Flashover

episodes.synopsis: When a teenager's boyfriend and another man both confess to her murder, the two accounts spawn a mystery that will take four decades to solve.
episodes.title: Dueling Confessions

episodes.synopsis: When a computer crash nearly ruins a prosperous company and its employees, investigators examine the possibility of human subterfuge.
episodes.title: Hack Attack

episodes.synopsis: A sleeping bag, a purse and a pair of bloody shoes lead police to a murdered young woman whose body bears a mark that could identify her killer.
episodes.title: Road Rage

episodes.synopsis: A woman walking her dogs in the woods is killed during deer hunting season, but strange clues, including a letter she wrote, complicate the case.
episodes.title: Hunter or Hunted?

episodes.synopsis: A popular television news anchor is shot outside her home. Authorities first suspect a stalker, until evidence leads them to question her husband.
episodes.title: News at 11

episodes.synopsis: Investigators blame a woman's death in a house fire on an unattended cigarette, until they learn her estranged husband is a police arson investigator.
episodes.title: Burning Desire

episodes.synopsis: A missing piece of duct tape turns out to be the crucial clue in a case involving murderous bank robbers who duct-taped a bank president to a chair.
episodes.title: Stick 'em Up

episodes.synopsis: A single dog hair is the pivotal clue leading investigators to the man who abducted and murdered a 16-year-old girl.
episodes.title: Making the Collar

episodes.synopsis: A couple's killer leaves new evidence as he attempts to cover his tracks, and investigators learn of a next-door neighbor's troubling secret past.
episodes.title: Palm Saturday

episodes.synopsis: A young mother's death appears to be a suicide, but suspicions are raised when the police learn she nearly died in a house fire three years earlier.
episodes.title: Army of Evidence

episodes.synopsis: A doctor says that he came home, found his wife bloody on the floor and tried to save her. But the blood spatter evidence suggests a different story.
episodes.title: Deadly Valentine

episodes.synopsis: A suspected runaway teen is found naked in a ditch miles from her home. Investigators study photographs and analyze weeds to track down her abductor.
episodes.title: Picture This

episodes.synopsis: When the car of a missing teen is dragged from a river, the interior is coated in motor oil. Can crash-test forensics help police unravel the mystery?
episodes.title: Oily in the Morning

episodes.synopsis: Investigators turn to forensic science for evidence in a murder case when two witnesses' descriptions of the culprit don't match the prime suspect.
episodes.title: A Clean Getaway

episodes.synopsis: Robbery appears to be the motive for an eccentric millionaire's murder, but investigators suspect that the evidence might tell another story.
episodes.title: Prints Among Thieves

episodes.synopsis: When a young woman is found decapitated, investigators analyze bloody gloves, irregular tire tracks and pine needles to zero in on the perpetrator.
episodes.title: Unholy Alliance

episodes.synopsis: Two murders in one town have police looking for a serial killer, and they catch a break when clues reveal a link between the victims.
episodes.title: Elemental Clue

episodes.synopsis: A killer murders a woman and leaves virtually no evidence, except for shoe prints. Can investigators use that sole clue to track down the murderer?
episodes.title: Sole Searching

episodes.synopsis: A stockbroker goes missing, and his car is found deserted near his office. With only a strange phone call to go on, police try to unravel the mystery.
episodes.title: Going for Broke

episodes.synopsis: Evidence implicates an ex-con in a brutal double homicide, but DNA taken from an ice cream spoon sends the investigation in an unexpected direction.
episodes.title: Just Desserts

episodes.synopsis: After a depressed woman seemingly commits suicide, police discover that she left behind a note that could help them track down her killer.
episodes.title: Murder, She Wrote

episodes.synopsis: When an aspiring model disappears, police use dog hair, a mixture of concrete and a forensic geologist to establish what happened.
episodes.title: Concrete Alibi

episodes.synopsis: Tiny fibers and an asthma inhaler prove to be the vital evidence investigators need to hunt down a gunman who shot an off-duty policeman.
episodes.title: Key Evidence

episodes.synopsis: When three young men are slain in a triple homicide, investigators follow a trail of clues that leads them to the seedy world of high-stakes gambling.
episodes.title: The Gambler

episodes.synopsis: The medical examiner rules a man's death an accident, but police think the scene was staged. Three years later, a second autopsy reveals the truth.
episodes.title: Undertaken

episodes.synopsis: After a hit-and-run boating accident kills a young man, investigators turn to the public for assistance and get help from an unexpected source.
episodes.title: Dark Waters

episodes.synopsis: After masked men shoot a husband and force his wife to open their hidden safe, investigators find evidence that leads them in an unexpected direction.
episodes.title: No Safe Place

episodes.synopsis: Investigators analyze minuscule paint chips and bits of plastic to search for the car that struck and killed a promising high school athlete.
episodes.title: Critical Maneuver

episodes.synopsis: Police are baffled when their investigation cannot determine how a killer entered or left the scene of a murder. Could he have vanished into thin air?
episodes.title: Insulated Evidence

episodes.synopsis: Jumbled evidence and too many suspects in a vicious murder thwart investigators, until clues reveal that the victim knew his killer.
episodes.title: Pressed for Crime

episodes.synopsis: A bloody fingerprint on a body could help police stop a serial killer, but first they must work out how to lift the print from the victim's skin.
episodes.title: Finger Pane

episodes.synopsis: Using cutting-edge forensic techniques, police use DNA extracted from a cigarette butt to identify the race, hair color and eye color of a killer.

episodes.synopsis: A woman's dogs were the only witnesses to her murder, and an expert in animal behavior sets out to see if they can help identify the killer.
episodes.title: Dog Day Afternoon

episodes.synopsis: Police find a criminal defense attorney slain in his own home amid a staged crime scene. Can a broken glass help identify the killer?
episodes.title: Shattered Innocence

episodes.synopsis: The murder of a college student went unsolved for more than a decade, until sophisticated new technology yielded fresh clues for investigators.
episodes.title: Jean Pool

episodes.synopsis: A woman is found dead shortly after seeking police protection following a road rage confrontation. Investigators think a cop might be the perpetrator.
episodes.title: Traffic Violations

episodes.synopsis: With the police stymied, a brother vows to catch the man who raped and killed his sister. Three decades later, DNA evidence helps him do just that.
episodes.title: Brotherly Love

episodes.synopsis: A teenage girl survives a bloody attack that claims the lives of her parents, but investigators begin to suspect that it was more than just luck.
episodes.title: Disrobed

episodes.synopsis: After a decade of remaining silent, a witness to the rape and murder of a hairdresser comes forward to help police reopen the investigation.
episodes.title: Driven to Silence

episodes.synopsis: Investigators try a key in every mailbox in a small California town and use a tire tread and broken jewelry to find the killer of a murdered teenager.
episodes.title: Weakest Link

episodes.synopsis: Sudden dense fog causes a 99-car accident and 12 deaths. Science will determine if the fog occurred naturally or was caused by industrial pollution.

episodes.synopsis: When a woman goes missing from her Phoenix home, police focus on her husband when an airline luggage tag and luminol point to an affair and murder.

episodes.synopsis: Handwriting and simple doodles turn an attempted murder bombing case into something very different in a peaceful British farming village.

episodes.synopsis: Bits of forensic evidence are the only clues for investigators who must first identify an incinerated body found in a dumpster, then catch the killer.

episodes.synopsis: Forensics experts uncover a bizarre tale linking a forged old document to three Salt Lake City bombings -- and a surprising potential perpetrator.

episodes.synopsis: The discovery of a boy's body near a stream in his Swiss village leads police to dredge the water for elusive clues that point to his killer.

episodes.synopsis: Analysis of key forensic evidence is needed in a Birmingham, Ala., case involving a judge who's killed in a bombing that may be linked to other cases.

episodes.synopsis: An Illinois couple is the focus of an investigation into a 1980s case in which a baby girl was kidnapped and murdered after an apparent home invasion.

episodes.synopsis: The 1984 rape of a young Virginia woman is revisited by the experts when DNA testing refutes her ID of the rapist and calls everything into question.

episodes.synopsis: Tiny paint specks from a little girl's pink bike and a sharp-eyed gym coach provide clues that could prove the case against an Arizona child murderer.

episodes.synopsis: Two years after a Michigan girl disappears, a suspect reveals the killer's name and motive -- but police must now match tiny blood spots to the crime.

episodes.synopsis: No body, no weapon, but no problem for a team of investigators who use forensics and detective work to prove a murder has taken place, and who did it.

episodes.synopsis: Experts try to unravel an arson case when a Seattle policeman's home is torched and a minor drug dealer disappears after confessing to the crime.

episodes.synopsis: How fresh is the evidence in a multiple rape and murder case? That's a question an FBI agent hopes to answer with his own vacuum cleaner experiment.

episodes.synopsis: The important role of fibers as forensic evidence is brought to life when a cold case is revived based on the discovery of unusual orange fibers.

episodes.synopsis: The English Channel yields a mystery that crosses the Atlantic when a fisherman finds a body in his net and investigators' best clue may be an anchor.

episodes.synopsis: A man's seemingly ordinary death from a heart attack turns into one of the most twisted cases of murder that local police have ever encountered.

episodes.synopsis: After forensic analysis confirms the identity of the body of a mutilated teenage girl, experts create a profile of the killer that's deadly accurate.

episodes.title: The Wilson Murder

episodes.synopsis: When residents of a South Dakota town develop similar, unexplained medical issues, researchers try to find the cause by focusing on one big family.
episodes.title: Outbreak

episodes.synopsis: After a young woman goes missing on the way to the train station, investigators use a strand of hair and a bloody pillowcase to identify a suspect.

episodes.synopsis: Police arrest a man when his wife is found mutilated the morning after a heated fight, but forensic evidence points to a different suspect.

episodes.synopsis: A man returns home from work to find his fiancée murdered. Using forensic odontology, police use bites on the woman's body to track down her killer.

episodes.synopsis: Decades after her mother vanished without a trace, a woman tells police that she witnessed her mom's death and knows where she is buried.

episodes.synopsis: A man says he returned to his hotel after a run to find his wife drowned in the bathtub. But a life insurance policy raises investigators' suspicions.

episodes.synopsis: The wife of a prominent dentist turns up dead, but the case stalls until a study of the weather on the night of the murder provides a vital clue.
episodes.title: Dew Process

episodes.synopsis: Police point the finger at a mentally troubled husband when his wife turns up dead, but an autopsy yields surprising results.
episodes.title: "Kill"igraphy

episodes.synopsis: A heart surgeon dies from a gunshot wound. Police aren't sure if it's suicide or homicide until they learn about his wife's explosive past.
episodes.title: Second Shot at Love

episodes.synopsis: When the murder of a store clerk is caught on blurry video, investigators combine old-school forensics with newfangled technology to nab the killer.
episodes.title: Video Diary

episodes.title: Missing in Time

episodes.synopsis: Breakthrough technology enables investigators to uncover a previously undetectable blood trail that leads to a grim discovery in a family's basement.

episodes.synopsis: A woman is accused of setting the fire that killed her son. Using the Internet, she mounts her own investigation and undermines the case against her.

episodes.synopsis: Investigating a dead body, police uncover a crime ring involving check scams, cattle auctions and vagrants, all run by a coldblooded elderly couple.
episodes.title: Killer's 'Cattle'log

episodes.synopsis: Fishing in a pond, two boys discover a human skull bearing marks of a heinous crime. Using DNA, police find clues to the victim and her killer.

episodes.synopsis: Years after a farmer's wife vanished without a trace, police call in plant pathologists to help them verify a lurid tale of murder down on the farm.

episodes.synopsis: After a female prison guard turns up dead, the medical examiner discovers a telltale clue from an old crime that puts an inmate under suspicion.
episodes.title: Pastoral Care

episodes.synopsis: When a thug attacks an off-duty state trooper, forensic evidence he leaves behind revives a strikingly similar case gone cold several states away.
episodes.title: Double Trouble

episodes.synopsis: After a pregnant woman dies from a gunshot to the head, blood spatter analysis helps police determine if it was an accident, suicide or murder.

episodes.synopsis: After a driver hits and permanently injures her young daughter, a mother uses the knowledge she's gleaned from crime shows to track down the culprit.
episodes.title: Treading Not So Lightly

episodes.synopsis: A mother and daughter vanish while out shopping. Scouring the store they visited for clues, investigators find evidence of a monstrous crime.

episodes.synopsis: A woman is found in an icy river, which washed away most evidence of her murder. But police find crucial clues in the DNA of the victim's son.
episodes.title: Who's Your Daddy?

episodes.synopsis: A forensic entomologist studies insects on a corpse to determine when the victim was killed and if the prime suspect could have done it.

episodes.synopsis: Acting on the coroner's findings, police go on the hunt for a pair of killers who repeatedly stabbed their victim before trying to cremate him.
episodes.title: Partners in Crime

episodes.synopsis: A girl starts running with a rough crowd, then vanishes. Police are stymied for over a decade until a cold case squad uncovers dramatic new evidence.
episodes.title: Cold Storage

episodes.synopsis: The murder of an elderly couple remains unsolved until a jeweler realizes that the victim's pendant necklace was pawned in her shop.
episodes.title: Elephant Tracks

episodes.synopsis: Investigators use wiretaps, cell phone mapping and other forensic tools to unravel the conspiracy behind the murder of a prominent surgeon.

episodes.synopsis: After a killer forces a woman into a car, a handwriting expert uses the signature on the car rental agreement to help police find the culprit.
episodes.title: Sign Here

episodes.synopsis: A murder suspect has videotape proof of his alibi. Police ask a physicist to examine the footage, and he discovers a surprising clue in the shadows.
episodes.title: Shadow of a Doubt

episodes.synopsis: A spate of violent robberies targeting tourists stymies police until a bite mark on a victim gives them the evidence they need to collar the culprit.
episodes.title: Tourist Trap

episodes.synopsis: A woman drowns, and the suspect claims it was an accident. But police identify striking similarities to another woman's death several states away.
episodes.title: All Wet

episodes.synopsis: After a nurse discovers that she is HIV-positive, cutting-edge investigative techniques determine who deliberately infected her and why.
episodes.title: Shot of Vengeance

episodes.synopsis: A killer murders a man and gravely injures two teenage girls, and police have just one clue to help them track down the culprit.
episodes.title: A Wrong Foot

episodes.synopsis: A young woman haunted by her mother's disappearance investigates 20 years later and discovers a dark family secret hidden inside a diary.
episodes.title: A Daughter's Journey

episodes.synopsis: When the body of a female student is found under an isolated highway ramp, an unusual clue leads San Diego police to a surprising suspect.
episodes.title: Badge of Betrayal

episodes.synopsis: A go-go dancer vanishes under suspicious circumstances. Decades later, her family still has no answers, until a phone call changes everything.
episodes.title: Deadly Matrimony

episodes.synopsis: A cigarette butt and a scrap of paper point the way to a dangerous pyromaniac who set 10 fires in California over a three-week period.
episodes.title: Point of Origin

episodes.synopsis: When a beloved nurse dies in a car crash and alcohol is ruled out as the cause, seedpods found in her hair and clothes prove it was murder.
episodes.title: Seeds for Doubt

episodes.synopsis: When three women disappear without a trace, DNA profiling and a talented forensic artist help the police link the crimes to a single predator.
episodes.title: Saving Face

episodes.synopsis: When hikers in Alaska discover a body wrapped in sheets with orange stitching, fabric fibers and ingenuity help them pick up the killer's trail.
episodes.title: Northern Exposure

episodes.synopsis: After a real estate tycoon leaves a will with instructions to follow in the event of his violent death, his skull is found riddled with bullets.
episodes.title: For Love or Money

episodes.synopsis: The murder of an American tourist at a Mexican resort brings investigative teams on both sides of the border together to uncover a sinister plan.
episodes.title: South of the Border

episodes.synopsis: A man seen stabbing his wife, pushing her into a swimming pool and holding her head under water claims he has no recollection of the crime.
episodes.title: Walking Terror

episodes.synopsis: Shards of a broken headlamp help police find a vehicle that fatally injured a Michigan cyclist before its driver fled the scene.
episodes.title: Plastic Puzzle

episodes.synopsis: When the evidence in a bombing goes up in smoke, savvy investigators find traces of proof the size of grains of sand that lead them to a murderer.
episodes.title: Tagging a Suspect

episodes.synopsis: When a military wife is found dead with a plastic bag near her face, investigators prove that what looked accidental was a carefully staged murder.
episodes.title: Strong Impressions

episodes.synopsis: When an arson fire destroys a home and a young boy is found dead 50 miles away, the search leads to a killer who left indisputable evidence.
episodes.title: Cereal Killer

episodes.synopsis: When the bodies of two victims are found in the same irrigation canal a year apart, police follow shoe prints on the trail of an unlikely killer.
episodes.title: A Leg Up on Crime

episodes.synopsis: Emergency dispatch receives a call from a man saying that his girlfriend shot and killed herself, but an autopsy reveals a very different story.
episodes.title: Gold Rush

episodes.synopsis: Evidence links the murder of a Navajo women who was killed with a sledgehammer to the nearby slaying of another Native American two years prior.
episodes.title: Four on the Floor

episodes.synopsis: Evidence in the case of a college student's death insinuates that he knew his killer, helping police unravel a web of lies and nab a murderer.
episodes.title: Cop Out

episodes.synopsis: A seemingly accidental drowning in an affluent suburb brings police to focus on one suspect who had a million reasons to want the victim dead.
episodes.title: Summer Obsession

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is found dead on a golf course in the Bahamas, a distinctive type of grass leads police to two suspects, each of whom blames the other.
episodes.title: Moss, Not Grass

episodes.synopsis: A teenager disappears after an evening of horseback riding. A month later, her body is found near her home, carrying clues that point to her killer.
episodes.title: Material Witness

episodes.synopsis: When a disc jockey is found dead in a community garden, a sniffer dog and a blood-splatter expert lead police to a killer who's too close for comfort.
episodes.title: Garden of Evil

episodes.synopsis: A muddy footprint sets investigators on the track of a ruthless killer who brutally murdered a victim who was asleep in bed.
episodes.title: Bump in the Night

episodes.synopsis: When the chef at a historic restaurant is slain and the usual suspects don't pan out, the evidence serves up a chilling tale of debt and deceit.
episodes.title: Murder on the Menu

episodes.synopsis: A rampaging serial arsonist sets multiple fires with the same type of device, which baffles investigators until clues arise from the ashes.
episodes.title: Hot on the Trail

episodes.synopsis: A coroner's inquest, paired with forensic science, gets to the truth behind a woman's apparent suicide and the involvement of her grieving spouse.
episodes.title: High 'n' Dry

episodes.synopsis: Investigators on both sides of the Atlantic bridge the distance to solve the puzzle of three related homicides that look like professional executions.
episodes.title: To the Viktor

episodes.synopsis: Detectives smoke out a skilled bomber with a motive for murder when a violent explosion kills a woman and sends shrapnel flying through the streets.
episodes.title: Wired for Disaster

episodes.synopsis: When a killer tries to incinerate and destroy proof of his crime, he unwittingly creates damning evidence only the newest technology can detect.
episodes.title: Wood-be Killer

episodes.synopsis: Incongruous evidence vexes police when two people are shot dead in a car, but a fingertip from a latex glove points to another crime scene.
episodes.title: Shattered Dreams

episodes.synopsis: A war veteran is found dead in his home, but the investigation grinds to a halt until a lucky break points to a shady character with a sweet tooth.
episodes.title: Dockter Visit

episodes.synopsis: When a driver pleads innocent to a hit-and-run crime, police locate a missing vehicle and find evidence that proves what really happened that night.
episodes.title: Capitol Crimes

episodes.synopsis: When a young man is killed in a mysterious car crash, the resulting evidence forces investigators to tell three families the devastating truth.
episodes.title: Grave Danger

episodes.synopsis: Tiny clues explain strange evidence at the scene of an unusual robbery-homicide, where the perpetrator ran out of the house, instead of breaking in.
episodes.title: A Case of the Flue

episodes.synopsis: A bomb constructed to inflict maximum damage kills a victim with deadly force, but tiny clues identify the murderer as if they bore his signature.
episodes.title: Live Wire

episodes.synopsis: When a man makes an emergency call to report his wife's injury in a fall, paramedics arrive to find a bloody crime scene that defies explanation.
episodes.title: A Novel Idea

episodes.synopsis: Fresh evidence from a 911 call revives a cold case in which the wife of a respected police officer was murdered in her home.
episodes.title: Chief Suspect

episodes.synopsis: A trio of ruthless killers thinks that a fire will cover their crime, but one tiny clue holds all the information needed to put them behind bars.
episodes.title: Shell Game

episodes.synopsis: The 10-year mystery of a college student's disappearance is solved when new forensic testing shines a different light on an elusive prime suspect.
episodes.title: Ring Him Up

episodes.synopsis: A woman's seemingly accidental death is reconsidered after a tipster calls police to suggest her husband killed her, then winds up dead himself.
episodes.title: Killer Impression

episodes.synopsis: When foul play befalls her father, a woman travels a thousand miles to find out what happened and who was behind it.
episodes.title: If I Were You

episodes.synopsis: When police try to figure out how a stalker acquired information about his victim, they find clues in a series of letters he sent to terrorize her.
episodes.title: A Tight Leash

episodes.synopsis: When an insurance assessor disappears while inspecting a storm-ravaged house, the police find evidence of a sloppy killer who left plenty of clues.
episodes.title: Muffled Cries

episodes.synopsis: When a woman vanishes hours after winning big at a casino and then turns up dead a month later, an anonymous phone call gives police their first lead.
episodes.title: Skirting the Evidence

episodes.synopsis: When a string of bombings terrorizes a small Colorado town, police examine the remnants of the bombs to track the culprit.
episodes.title: Small Town Terror

episodes.synopsis: New forensic technology -- including DNA profiling -- enables authorities to reopen the investigation into a 20-year-old murder case.
episodes.title: Fresh Heir

episodes.synopsis: Evidence and witness testimony conflict when a fall down a flight of stairs kills a socialite, leaving the final determination up to forensic experts.
episodes.title: Step by Step

episodes.synopsis: Carpet and blanket fibers, coupled with unique wax bullets, help forensic experts track down the man who killed a department-store clerk.
episodes.title: Blanket of Evidence

episodes.synopsis: When a woman's body is found in a burned-out house, microscopic clues on a piece of pipe help determine whether her death was an accident or murder.
episodes.title: Fired-Up

episodes.synopsis: Three years after the murders of a millionaire and his family, new clues -- including a decades-old box of ammunition -- point to the killer.
episodes.title: Two in a Million

episodes.synopsis: This episode re-examines the 1960 kidnapping and murder of brewery heir Adolph Coors III through the lens of modern forensic techniques.
episodes.title: Bitter Brew

episodes.synopsis: When the prime suspect in a young girl's murder is sent to prison, high-tech tools from NASA help prove that the wrong man is serving time.
episodes.title: Sharper Image

episodes.synopsis: Investigators track the clues left behind by a missing woman, including surveillance footage of what may have been her last hours on earth.
episodes.title: Wheel of Misfortune

episodes.synopsis: More than 10 years after the slaying of a Seattle musician, DNA evidence collected at the time of the crime becomes vital to solving the case.
episodes.title: The Day the Music Died

episodes.synopsis: When a graduate student disappears and is presumed dead, a geology professor at Michigan State University lends his special expertise to the case.
episodes.title: Sole Survivor

episodes.synopsis: A spurned would-be lover may be behind the death of a woman gunned down in her driveway, but it won't be easy to prove the young man was obsessed.
episodes.title: Catch 22

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is raped and murdered on the beach, investigators track down the killer through a pair of shoes left near the body.
episodes.title: A Cinderella Story

episodes.synopsis: Eight years after the rape and murder of a college student, a cell phone and some running shoes help investigators crack the cold case.
episodes.title: Sands of Crime

episodes.synopsis: Investigators believe that a missing college student will turn up -- until they find blood evidence that her boyfriend has tried to cover up.
episodes.title: Sworded Scheme

episodes.synopsis: A unique button and some of its connecting threads are investigators' only clues when a woman is stabbed more than 30 times.
episodes.title: Fashion Police

episodes.synopsis: When a woman disappears after evening church services, police search for a mysterious van that several witnesses saw her step into.
episodes.title: Church Dis-service

episodes.synopsis: Weeks after a young girl vanishes, a psychic leads investigators to a field, where they find her body and clues to her killer's identity.
episodes.title: Seedy Intentions

episodes.synopsis: When forensic specialists enhance surveillance footage, they discover that a seemingly simple encounter is instead an abduction by a serial killer.
episodes.title: DNA Dragnet

episodes.synopsis: When a surgeon is stabbed to death, the prime suspect has an alibi -- until the investigation uncovers a conspiracy behind the murder.
episodes.title: Office Visit

episodes.synopsis: At an apartment where a mother was stabbed to death, investigators find plenty of evidence but have no suspect to compare it against.
episodes.title: Shoe-in for Murder

episodes.synopsis: A family of four is gunned down in what appears to be an interrupted robbery, but police discover a far more heinous motive behind the attack.
episodes.title: Family Interrupted

episodes.synopsis: When a woman with more than 50 stab wounds is found floating in a harbor, are her missing ex and daughter also victims, or did they commit the murder?
episodes.title: Runaway Love

episodes.synopsis: When the prime suspect in a park ranger's murder is quickly cleared, nearly six years elapse before DNA technology brings new facts to light.
episodes.title: Watchful Eye

episodes.synopsis: Authorities don't have much to go on when a rapist and murderer spends hours cleaning up the crime scene and then disposes of the body.
episodes.title: Waste Mis-Management

episodes.synopsis: A week after a couple vanishes during a Memorial Day beach trip, a seemingly unrelated robbery leads authorities to new clues.
episodes.title: Dirty Little Seacret

episodes.synopsis: After a young mother is killed and her 4-year-old daughter brutally assaulted, it takes 15 years until DNA technology can identify the culprit.
episodes.title: Lights Out

episodes.synopsis: A woman's rapist and murderer is brought to justice with evidence from an unlikely source: a hamburger bun.
episodes.title: Purebread Murder

episodes.synopsis: When numerous clues bring investigators to a murder scene, evidence is plentiful -- but the victim's body is nowhere to be found.
episodes.title: Hear No Evil

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is shot to death in a church parking lot, police zero in on her spouse, who recently learned she'd been having an affair for three years.
episodes.title: Three's a Crowd

episodes.synopsis: When a man dies after a hydraulic jack slips and drops a truck on him, investigators soon discover that it wasn't just a tragic accident.
episodes.title: A Squire's Riches

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is beaten to death a month after her husband saves her from a fire, evidence points to an intruder -- but authorities have their doubts.
episodes.title: Home of the Brave

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is slain, police suspect her philandering fiancé until a third party steps forward with a surprising revelation about the murder weapon.
episodes.title: Textbook Murder

episodes.synopsis: A missing teenage girl's family hopes that she just ran away, but the discovery of her body confirms their worst fears and sends police on a manhunt.
episodes.title: Filtered Out

episodes.synopsis: The bodies of a woman and her two daughters are found floating in Tampa Bay, leading to a high-profile manhunt.
episodes.title: Water Logged

episodes.synopsis: When four young people are slaughtered in an upscale Texas community, neighbors give authorities descriptions of two strangers seen in the area.
episodes.title: Social Circle
